Pod-Term version 0.01
=====================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Pod::Simple
    Term::ANSIColor
    Carp
    Clone
    Hash::Merge

The following modules are also required for testing:

    Pod::Simple
    Test::More
    

